Title: Feeling Minnesota
Actors: Keanu Reeves, Cameron Diaz, Vincent D'Onofrio, Delroy Lindo
Plot: Freddie is a former stripper marrying Sam to repay a debt owed to nightclub owner Red. But Freddie is in love with Jjaks, Sam's brother. Jjaks and Freddie run off together, and Sam finds where they have been hiding and calls the cops. Meanwhile someone calls to blackmail Sam and Jjaks. In the end will it all work out?
